    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty from day one\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend with the good stuff. It honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There\u2019s a tiny, barely-visible stone chip on the hood from a mountain drive, but that\u2019s just a little bit of character on an otherwise flawless ride! I\u2019m only letting her go to a good home where she'll be loved just as much. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
