      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2011 BMW M3 (E92) finished in Interlagos Blue. This S65-powered masterpiece is mechanically flawless, featuring a high-revving 4.0L V8 that has been fastidiously maintained. Preventative maintenance is fully addressed: rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells and ARP bolts, and throttle actuators upgraded to gear-driven units for permanent reliability. The M-DCT gearbox has been optimized with a GTS software flash for crisper downshifts and improved clamping force. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functioning perfectly, complemented by fresh bushings and Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber on all four corners. No subframe cracks, no VANOS rattle, and zero oil consumption. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating. This is a turn-key, investment-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    }
